Recent hang with friends @jehbk and @msttunie who you recently saw play @cissyhouston_ to rave reviews in the biopic. Proudly helped the #lawandorder alum prepare for that #iwannadancewithsomebody role with my personal memories of #cissyhouston and #whitneyhouston.

The chameleon is currently playing a Hatian matriarch and Brooklyn-based grandmother of five in the play #bernardasdaughters at @signatureinnyc #signaturetheatre. Catch her fire, passion, strength and wisdom up close and personal in this intimate theater. Play closes June 3rd!

Love you Tam!! #friendship #gordonchambers #tamaratunie #hatianamericans #westbankcafe

Theater lovers, the latest @mtc_nyc production KING JAMES at the New York City Center is also one NOT to miss. What a beautiful,  clearly written two-character play about an unexpected interracial friendship between two fans of #lebronjames who argue incessantly about his leaving and return to Cleveland. Of course, the issues run deeper. Well done!

Great to meet Puerto Rican acting power couple @zz_nyc #davidzayas (“Dexter”) and @lizacolonzayas_lcz (“Orange Is The New Black” and “The Bear”) whose work I’ve thoroughly enjoyed on stage and screen. They loved the play as much as I did! 

Bravo to the cast, producers and ubiquitous director @iamkennyleon #kingjames #manhattantheatreclub

Wedding Flow: ‘Twas perfect weather and blue skies indeed for a Brooklyn #redhook rooftop wedding! Congrats gorgeous bride Kendra who became Mrs. @cheyennebostock today. I sang @steviewonderlegacy #ribboninthesky and these two string players did the processional music. They head to @berkleecollege next year! Excited for their journey! 

#gordonchambers #cheyennebostock #steviewonder

TBT: spent a glorious #memorialday with three generations of family yesterday. We all enjoyed my six young cousins who call me Uncle Gordon on Aunt Joan’s 52nd wedding anniversary to Uncle Peter Elliston. Rest in peace, peacemaker.

Uncle Fred Powell, a former US Veteran, ascended six years ago today. I vividly remember speaking and performing at the @apollotheater the night of his homegoing knowing that is exactly where he would want me to be. Rest in power, man of empowerment.

So grateful for the #unclelove and encouragement I received from the these men as a child that allows me to give it to many youth today! #familymatters❤️

Soooo grateful to @herharlematelier for this thank you note and for seeing the educator, public speaker, moderator in me before I claimed that space for myself. Speaking and conducting workshops for her with the @apolloedharlem at the @apolloedharlem has been SUCH an honor. All the best to you sister in your next chapter. #gordonchambers #musiceducation #apollotheater #apolloeducation

Thank you @jaayparks! Singers, DM and let’s begin your lesson journey!!

When emotional and spiritual sounds are developing within your own voice and you realize how dope and healthy the results can be is a one in a million feeling! @gordonchambers #artistdevelopment #singboy #vocalcoach #lessismore #bestteacher

FBF: Continued #unclelove this week! Thankful to my friend @fridayarts for sending me an article in the UK @bbcnews which celebrated my young British born cousin/nephew @jordsonline new hip hop album release on @motownrecords! The article gave me and his dad drummer Barry (whose former band toured with Sade) shoutouts. Great to see them last December in London. #familytime #blacklondon 

Also spent quality time this week with my young cousin/nephews MJ and Matthew this week due to their mom @jodiawatson surprise visit. So grown and smart! #jamaicanfamilyvalues What an honor to be a role model to the next generation of music makers and future leaders. Congrats #jords #jordanwilkes #motownrecords. Shine on and make us proud🇯🇲🇺🇸

Thank you @jjhamptons and #winstonwatt, my parents best man for their 1968 wedding, both memorialized yesterday in Harlem and Montego Bay, for the lives you lived, the love you gave and the legacies you’ve left here on Earth for us to continue following. Her friend circle celebrated all day long, as she would have desired. 

Was honored to sing my original song “Circle Of Love” from my Surrender album and “That’s What Friends Are For” for Joyce’s service and help Mommy prepare her remarks that were included virtually in the service in Jamaica. Also to my great surprise, Joyce’s son Brandon chose this picture I took of her for the back side of the program. Let’s cherish our friends and family and live each day to the fullest. Tomorrow is not promised. Love don’t cost a thing❤️ Live and Give🙏🏿

TBT: Thank you so much @sydjcolson of the #losvegasaces for this backstage #blackgirlmagic #wnba serenade to #anitabaker last week that went viral! It’s been viewed almost 2 million times actually. It means the world to me to have lived long enough by Gods grace to see my catalog touch 3 generations. 

Brought back memories of Auntie Anita dedicating #iapologize to my parents for their 30th anniversary years ago in Atlantic City and she and @iamsylviarhone and the Elektra Record staff being so gracious to us backstage. Dreams come true. Continued success to THE SONGSTRESS who changed my life on her national tour. #gordonchambers. Happy #blackmusicmonth #sydneycolson

Happy heavenly 65th birthday @prince! A spring 2019 pop-up performance of “Pop Life” with my bro artiste and bandleader extraordinaire @chrisrobonline and friends. Grateful to the maestro for his lyrical brilliance, instrumental excellence and style du jour! His purple soul power still reigns. #gordonchambers #princerogersnelson #chrisrob #nublunyc #livemusic #paisleypark #prince #poplife

Memories of writing “One Voice” that I shared in an interview with @midnightrnbedition! Her interview site is helping @brandy celebrate the 25th anniversary of the release of the iconic album “Never Say Never” which went diamond the US this year (10x platinum) and has sold almost 17x platinum worldwide! Congrats ladies! #brandynorwood #gordonchambers

Congrats to all the amazing contributors of “Never Say Never” which celebrates its 25th anniversary today. I shared in my debut interview with @midnightrnbedition my experience of the day my co-writer Phil Gladston played me the @davidfoster production of “One Voice”. 

We had originally intended #onevoice for  @celinedion but A&R @craigkallman but picked it first  for @brandy. I was moved to tears by how her innocent tone seemed to float over the choir #bebewinans had assembled. So proud of all that she and her primary producer @rodneyjerkins continue to do in this industry. 

Keep shining your light @midnightrnbedition and celebrating music! Happy #blackmusicmonth all! #gordonchambers #brandynorwood 
#rodneyjerkins #philgaldston #craigkallman #atlanticrecords

I looooove living in Brooklyn. One of the most fascinating and memorable dining experiences in my borough last night eating #nigerianfood with home-cooking flair with four old friends and meeting 12 new fellow foodies at at @deptofculturebk! #jamesbeardfoundation 

Congrats to the chef/owner and his tiny team with BIG dreams and hearts on their prestigious @beardfoundation #jamesbeardfoundation nomination. This goat soap reminded me of family outings in Jamaica, where parties ONLY and always begin with a cup of spicy soup. Delicious delicious! Thank you #departmentofculture #bedstuy #foodieheaven

I am both a musician, music educator, a music lover and a perpetual music student for lifetime! I so so love IG pages like @misssharid @soulmusicsociety @90s.mood_ @ronniehall_the_vocalcoach @kimnicky that share the bounty and brilliance of great music! Thank y’all!❤️🙏🏿👏 Stop, look, listen and learn. 🎵🎵🍾🍾🍾👑👑

From gospel to blues to doo-Wop to rock-and-roll to R&B, we bring harmony and joy to the world. Behold all of this brilliance and be uplifted. Happy Sunday! Happy #blackmusicmonth. Happy #pridemonth. Sing @whitneyhouston @cissyhouston_ @tinaturner @averywilson @brownstoneofficial . RIP Kenny Moore (Tina’s amazing pianist who passed in 1997 at 45).

A friend of @valeriesashford is a friend of mine! Thanks to all the fabulous folks who came out last night for my fourth time hosting @sugarbarnyc #openmike. I felt the spirit of @rongrantnfriends (RIP) with Tony Stevenson on bass.

Thank you @raychewlive @ashtnmrtn @theartofolu_ @yvetteconcuatro @youbettaknowdebbiemcintyre @damara_lynn_greene @selanonline for your warm smiles, well wishes and happy energy all night long!

I sing because I’m happy, I sing because I’m free!

Congrats to MD @raychewlive extraordinaire on the amazing Macys Parade music tributes on 4th of July. We needed that! Also….FYI: Tonight @iammeloniedaniels @thisisryanshaw @darius_booker_nyc will be at @sugarbarnyc for “When Singers Meet”. 

Happy Friday all!❤️🙏🏿❤️🎵

#gordonchambers 
#raychew 
#sugarbarnyc

Scenes from Thursday night when I hosted #openmike at the @sugarbarnyc and last night when @darius_booker_nyc @iammeloniedaniels @thisisryanshaw cohosted “When Singers Meet” where @sashaallenmusic and @dwarrensings wore us OUT. 

Hearing @william.barnes.984 “Bygones” live brought me to tears. I heard this song for years live at @rongrantnfriends “Village Underground” Sunday night open mike before this guitar whiz produced it for my Love Stories album which dear friends of decades Mel, Darius and Ryan all sang backgrounds on.

So grateful to the @ashfordandsimpson @valeriesashford for the inspiration of their musical catalogue to us all, and their legendary hospitality at this beloved eatery. Long live legend Valerie Simpson.

Thanks for posting this @blackmusiccollective! HBD @niccigilbert of @brownstoneofficial. Memories of performing this live on BET “Video Soul”. Big wheels keep on turning.
Thanks for putting this back in the set list for your tour! 

#gordonchambers #niccigilbert #halfofyou #fromthebottomup

This tree trunk gave me shelter from the raindrops yesterday, but I stayed til the end to dance to the grand finale song @steviewonderlegacy #anotherstar (which features @bobbihumphrey on flute and @georgebensonguitar on guitar!)!

Thank you for @soulsummitmusic for this annual #housemusic dance party reunion and @superbizzee for footage of me in freedom dance releasing stress! No place like NYC for #hotfuninthesummertime!

Always TRULY grateful for the respect the younger brethren in my life bestow on me, the “OG” GC (as they often call me). Thanks all for great recent hangs, summer happy meals and conversations of inspiration @scrupulous_shujaa @jovanid_ @iamsteffreed @superbizzee @sellocnn actor and birthday boy @tomlukedicostanzo @tacai_dryden @trainerbrad. Nuff respect to all of you for going for your goals and dreams with passion and fashion! #brotherhood

Last and not least, RIP Cyrus. Thank you  @octaviusterry for choosing “Missing You” to tribute this 30-year-old I didn’t get a chance to meet. Condolences to all the families. Tomorrow is not promised. Spread love everyday.❤️❤️❤️🙏🏿🙏🏿

#gordonchambers 
#missingyou

You know it’s summer when I’m spending some time in #sagharbor! Recent scenes from a beautiful lunch hosted by @jehbk where I bumped into my former @essence coworker @harriettecole. Look out for us in the five-episode documentary called “Time of Essence: Fifty Years of Defining Culture” that will debut on @owntv on August 18th. Thanks for hosting, JoJo! #essencemagazine #owntv #gordonchambers #harriettecole #joannehill

Thank you @sholaadisafarrar for your kind words! Always brings me great joy #vocalcoaching actors. They truly understand the assignment is to tell the story of the song with your voice! Express yourselves this summer! DM for lesson inquiries, in person or virtual. Stay hydrated. Great day all!

My European summer 2023 adventures continues! Good morning from #ibiza, a long time bucket list weekend trip. Views from the lodging rooftop, the local baguette cafe, the graffiti-lined side streets—scenes from my morning walk.

RIP #georgemichael and thank you #andrewridgeley for bravely telling your wild and wonderful #wham stories, including shooting a music video here for “Club Tropicana” on this dance-music haven of an island off the coast of Spain. #wham #blackswhotravel 

What a beautiful friendship and heartfelt @whamofficial Netflix documentary. A must must see!

Life’s a beach and then you die—and this one is stunning indeed! A friend of @jacquifrancis9 is a friend of mine. Great fun with @summerloving71 all day yesterday who DJ’d a set of the #ibizaartfair. 

We then headed to the swanky local @thestandard hotel for a scrumptious dinner arranged by @jenniferlouisefoley. The young actress @madeline00shields that I coach truly has the coolest Mama bear ever. #jenniferlouisfoley

Thank you #ibiza for #dayparty #funinthesun #gordonchambers #adrianloving #ibizabeaches #ibizaspain #thestandardibiza #islandsofspain

Oh what a night! Thank you so much humble music royalty @louievega for inviting @jacquifrancis9 and @summerloving71 and I to see
legends @realblackcoffee and @therealdjmanoo spin at the world-famous @hiibizaofficial. This club had a lighting show and sound system like  NONE other I’ve ever seen and heard. Amazing to see these DJs like #louievega book summer-long residencies at clubs that hold 1000s. Countdown til I see @beyonce in NJ.

#dancemusic, once a subculture Black and LGBTQ NYC underground genre, is now a multi-billion dollar industry.Truly something like a phenomenon.

#littlelouievega #blackcoffeedj #manoo #dancemusicculture #hiibiza

Got off the beach-by-day club-by-night #ibiza schedule yesterday to take in the history and beauty of this magical island off the coast of Spain! Thank you @airbnbexperiences for the gift of captain Basilio who sailed myself and the joyous conservation biologist Tamara and powerhouse cancer survivor-turned-patient advocate Christina by sunset. We headed back to #thestandardibiza rooftop for a final nightcap. Happiness while traveling is very often the wonderful strangers you meet. Thank you @airbnb and @jenniferlouisefoley and @thestandard. 

#airbnbexperiences #sanantoniobayibiza 
#sailboating

Ibiza started opening its discos in the 70s but long long before this multicultural hippie scene began, the melinated Moors and Phoenicians also occupied and governed this island. Spain and so much of Europe is far more brown than it wants to think of itself as. Thoroughly enjoyed learning about centuries of war and resistance over these territories with European colonizers that took place just outside of the foreboding high walls of the Old Town where we stayed. #oldtownibiza #airbnbexperiences 

The views from up top of the most expensive yacht port in the world were stunning. The Old City now has beautiful boutiques (that sell #phoenician memorabilia), Michelin restaurants and five star hotels. Once again, thank you @airbnbexperiences for an opportunity to lean something deeper about this island than the discotheques. #blackswhotravel

Couldn’t DARE leave #ibiza without having a quick sip and dip in this famous pool at the joyfully slightly infamous @pikesibiza hotel, owned by #tonypike —former lover of @gracejonesofficial, great friend of @freddiemercury and frequent host to @whamofficial. They the recorded their “Club Tropicana”’music video here during the peak of their pop reign of the youth. Thanks @superbizzee for making sure I stopped by! #blackswhotravel 

It is a serious HEATWAVE in Spain! #globalwarming is a seemingly here to stay. Eat light, swim lots and stay hydrated and we enjoy the summer of 2023! Thank you @samanthamonteithstyle for the invite, #pikeshotel for your legendary hospitality and #georgemichael for your fabulous catalogue. #tonypike #gracejones

Whenever I’m traveling I take a morning gratitude walk.Scenes from final day in Spain. I thank God for my limbs, the peeps I love and for a life filled daily with the gift of the pursuit of happiness. #laramblabarcelona

Scenes from yesterdays afternoon @airbnbexperiences tour with Luke of the 2000-year old streets of #barcelona. Amazing tales about the wars, the Moors, the Romans, the Catholics, the Royals who funded Christopher Columbus, the proud secessionist Catalans, the Colonizers, the Musuems, the shopkeepers, the Artisans including Picasso who’ve made these streets home. Fascinating was an understatement. #blackswhotravel #oldcitybarcelona

My guest on the podcast today is singer-songwriter-producer and recording artist @gordonchambers. 

His #1 hits as a lyricist include: Anita Baker’s Grammy- winning hit “I Apologize”, Brownstone’s Grammy-nominated “If You Love Me”, Angie Stone’s “No More Rain (In This Cloud)”, the Grammy-nominated theme of Set It Off “Missing You” (performed by Brandy, Tamia, Gladys Knight and Chaka Khan).

In our wide ranging conversation, Gordon and I chat about his upbringing in New Jersey, the concept of Black excellence, working at Essence Magazine, the mentorship of Susan Taylor and Phyllis Hyman, his successful career in music , the power of Love and his embrace of Blackness. Listen now on ALL major podcast platforms and watch on YouTube. #podcast #podcastersofinstagram #podcasting #blackpod #blackpodcasters #talkshow #music #blackmusic #essencemagazine

TRIBUTE: Thank you for all the calls y’all. Today my heart completely shattered when I heard that my beautiful brother from another mother @mrjoness3 transitioned. Whether on stage, in studio or just kicking it this friend of mine made me feel completely free, supported, respected, prayed for and always unconditionally loved. ❤️🙏🏿❤️🙏🏿🎵❤️🙏🏿🎵

Met #danieljones through @shedrickmitchellofficial and befriended @chinahblac @jermaine_parrish @dwiskingbeef_official @catalystmusic Jeremy Most Mike Severson and many others through him. Sad to see him go so soon but proud to have loved him from day one when I he played for my debut release concert of Introducing Gordon Chambers at Bb Kings in 2003. 
@erro44, host of @sobsnyc Sol Village for which Daniel was MD for a decade, said it so well: “He was the person I trusted most on stage.” In 20 years I saw him stay humble and grounded as he rose to play keys and become MD to icons like @janetjackson @erykahbadu @justintimberlake @therealmaryjblige. He ALWAYS got me a ticket to these shows to thank me for being a support to him in the early days. We also went to many fabulous dinners afterwards at his beloved Blue Ribbon. He was a serious foodie who also loved to cook up a storm for friends and family. #ericroberson 

Proud of the husband and father he became, the suburban homeowner, the fabulous event-thrower in Dallas. Final clip is me singing for his birthday in February for his hometown extravaganza. What a joyous night. Wouldn’t ever imagine would be the last time I would see him but he was happy as a lark that night—hence I am praying to accept God’s will. 

Thank you Samuel III (his rockstar artist nickname) for choosing me as family and mentor. Grateful for your light, your loud Southern “Ole Cliff” laughter, your effortless musical brilliance, your prayers, your prophetic wisdom, your loyal and unconditional love as a friend. Prayers to your wife, sons, twin brothers, Mom, Grandmother, Uncles and the whole Jones clan. 

To know you was to LOVE you. And how sweet is now is to be loved by you from above where you now rest with the Most High.  #gordonchambers #friendship #sobsnyc

TBT: went down memory lane and found a video of me playing with with the late great MD @mrjoness3 @jermaine_parrish @catalystmusic and #mikeseverson. We had sooo much fun. Jeremy Most also played guitar with us during this period of my live gigs in NYC. #danieljones also co-wrote “Still Blessing Me” with @jermaine.hardsoul @hak.young and I. 

The cut that moves me most is this spontaneous rendition at the Blue Note of the gospel classic “Walk With Me”. Daniel just followed along with the most melodic and comforting chords. Spoke to all these gents he loved yesterday. We are all in shock but supporting each other through it. RIP King Jones. Heaven has gained a piano and organ and synth man to lead the band above. Until we meet again.❤️🙏🏿🥲🎵

Flashback Friday: Another live clip at the @bluenotenyc  with @catalystmusic @jermaine_parrish #mikeseverson  and MD #danieljones @mrjoness3 on acoustic piano. “I’ll Miss You Most” is a deeply emotional ballad from my debut album. Daniel and this crew also played with such grace and class even at young ages. They learned songs from the inside out and put their own swag and spin on them. Daniel felt music, set tempos, reharmonized chords spontaneously in ways that added feeling and unexpected colors. This song about the loneliness performers quietly feel always moved him. Happy birthday Mitch who’s on bass here. 

I dedicate this to this now late great keyboard whiz and also to crooner #tonybennett who transitioned today at 96 Billie Holliday also transitioned on July 17. They, too, graced this iconic stage. He was fluent in every genre, but in many ways, Daniel was a jazz man with a pop resume that spun from Jay Z, Beyoncé; Rihanna, Ja’Net Jackson, Erykah Badu, Justin Timberlake, Eve, Joe, Mary J Blige to hundreds of indie artists whom he gave EQUAL time, care and attention to when collaborating. Thank you for our beautiful memories King Jones. I love you little brother now “where there is no space and time” as Donny sang. 

#gordonchambers #danieljones #thebluenotenyc #illmissyoumost #introducinggordonchambers
Countdown: friendship reunion tonight! Excited to see @iamsuch in concert tonight in my city. She brought me to Denver in April. Showtime at 730 pm at @citywinerynyc! #citywinerynyc

It felt only right to spend my weekend with other loved ones of the late GREAT Dallas-born church-trained keyboard whiz #danieljones @mrjoness3. Great to hear his bros @jermaine_parrish on drums and @aliasboogie on bass today who I’ve shared many stages with alongside Daniel. 

They played at @agaperahway this morning where @lorendawson is MD and @william.barnes.984 was on guitar. @iamleonlacey was also in the building, and ironically was with me the last time we both saw Daniel. Also broke bread with @chinahblac and @barkimmusic1 and worshiped with @geneanjones, Daniels cousin. Even in grief, we still have faith in God to see us through it. We will still bless the Lords name. He is always worthy to be praised. ❤️💪❤️🙏🏿🎵🙏🏿
#agapefamilyworshipcenter #jermaineparrish

Recent #vocalcoching scenes from day one with singer-songwriter-playwright @summerrona who wrote these kind words, @mdm.negritabonita and singer-actress @sholaadisafarrar. #voicelessons #selfexpression #musiceducation #summerrona #artistdevelopment 

Ladies, your voices and energy lift me up—even through last weeks airport FaceTime @sholaadisafarrar! Thank you❤️🙏🏿❤️🙏🏿👍🏿🎵👏 #gordonchambers

Also felt right to celebrate a room that @mrjoness3 #danieljones (RIP) MD’d #solvillage at for so many years last night. Thank you Larry Gold, family and staff for 40 years of presenting live music at #sobsnyc. I was overwhelmed at the history of this downtown #livemusic establishment. I remember coming here to see early mentors @phyllishyman and #abbeylincoln long before headlining this room many times. What amazing memories playing here with Daniel, @dwiskingbeef_official, @jermaine_parrish #jeremymost and many more musical brethren of mine.

TBT: This has been a week of mourning but also a worldwide celebration of the late GREAT #danieljones: keyboard whiz, MD, artist, writer-producer (Beyoncé, Rihanna) and most importantly FRIEND to so many. He curated community effortlessly.

Enjoy these reposted clips of him in his MD magic in the @janetjackson rehearsals and @justintimberlake pre-show huddles beaming his light while striking up the band. Thank you @erykahbadu for having his hometown Dallas stadium shout his name on the final show of your tour he would have played. 

Thank you DJ for the support you gave on stage and in the studio to indie artists like myself and @sainttiz. Thank you @sobsnyc for the platform and the memories of seeing him on stage with The Collective at #solvillage that built his chops for icons later in his journey. Thank you @dwiskingbeef_official for informing me last Wednesday minutes after heaven called him home.

Most of all, thank you Mr. Jones for choosing me as big brother. The love you gave me lives on and on. We love you King and will tell all til the day we die about how deeply you touched our lives. Please keep the Jones family in prayer. Rest in power Dallas Deacon of Joy Daniel Jones.

#friendship #blackexcellence #janetjackson #justintimberlake #gordonchambers #sobsnyc #erykahbadu #dallas #saintiz

Flashback Friday: almost forgot what a good time I had just two weeks ago in #ibiza and #barcelona and #spain. This year I’ve already lost four friends, but also met some friendly strangers in my travels and made new amigos en #españa . Grateful. Tomorrow is NOT promised. Live, love, forgive and make memories you’ll cherish EVERYDAY❤️🙏🏿

Thanks again @jacquifrancis9 and @summerloving71. We’ll do something fun next summer for sure! #blackwhotravel #airbnbexperiences #friendship

Happy Sunday! It continues to comfort me to spend time with other loved ones of the late GREAT #danieljones. Great to hang last night with music exec and old friend @joeyharrisinc who recently worked closely with Daniel on the @janetjackson TOGETHER AGAIN tour. Was glad to be able to help him find a last minute showcase venue for these two amazing young singer-songwriters @jonojono_official and @austinholmess. Enjoyed you both! Thank you @brooklynmusickitchen for answering the call. #brooklynmusickitchen #joeyharris #janetjackson 

Deacon Jones (my new heavenly nickname for him) often reminded the impact I’ve made on younger musicians. I am clear on the assignment you left me Sir. Thank you DJ for introducing me to a fellow Dallas-born singer-songwriter @sainttiz who I had brunch with yesterday at @acehotelbrooklyn. We creatives must encourage each other. Beautiful sit-down #gordonchambers #friendship #mentoring

Countdown! We bout to release our wiggles! With cuzzo Lady Tee (family nickname) @taraflorabella about to see Queen B @beyonce! What a pre-show fashion extravaganza! Trivia fact: when Labelle played the Metropolitan Opera House in the mid-70s, the theme was “Wear Something Silver.” Somehow that also happened tonight! Thanks Jonita for organizing. #suitelife #beyonce
Spellbinding visual beauty. What an aesthetic storyteller. What colors, palettes and clothing she presented and inspired from the audience. On such a high, I can’t sleep! Thank you @beyonce

SALUTE: She started with a ballad set, reminding us that she is a SINGER with perfect pitch, unique tones, cascading bluesy riffs and one who idolizes the greats before her. #imgoingdown 

She returned with the multiple outfit changes for the Renaissance longer segment with the stunning sets, the acrobatic dancers, the brilliant band and singers, the phenomenal camera work and the state-of-the-art production. And on top of that, when the tempo sped up, she still sang flawlessly for two hours plus and conveyed amazing poise, gratitude and pure love to the audience. She’s living her best life, giving her grandest tour, empowering her daughter and slaying with amazing grace.

I was just amazed! Thank you #beyonce. So proud to be a part of her transition into solo stardom as co-writer of “After All Is Said And Done.” After all is said and done, she will go down in history as the best of this century to do this. Thank you Uncle Johnny for making that dress that inspired her to dream this BIG!

What JOY to see my Brooklyn neighbor @jonbatiste 5x Grammy, Golden Globe and Oscar winner lead a masterclass at @bmsbrooklyn today! His energy is just infectious and his #jazz talent otherworldly. New Orleans finest is now a King of Kindness in Kings County. Thanks for inviting me @nolanbaynes. Music education builds confidence❤️

Salute to you the Big Easy born jazz wizard for giving back! A friend of @reallouiscato and @aulstontaylor is a friend of mine! #jonbaptiste #gordonchambers #brooklynmusicschool #fortgreenebrooklyn

Flashback Friday: What FUN we had, often playing @sobsnyc @bluenotenyc and Tristate road-trips! See you soon @catalystmusic. Thanks for the memories on-stage and off @mrjoness3. To Dallas I now go for the homegoing. May the healing begin for his family and thousands of beloved friends and colleagues. #danieljones Thank you @colabolabooks for many prayers before these shows and this morning. Thank you for loving my tribe —in life and now transition —over the decades ❤️❤️🙏🏿🙏🏿❤️❤️

Throwback: my fiftieth birthday with @reggievanlee and @vanliemptbrown at @goldbarnewyork. RIP @jjhamptons who transitioned at 75 earlier this year. Happy 76th to the phenomenal woman @lolacee. Stay forever young!

To know him was to LOVE him. We came thousands thick to celebrate the amazingly accomplished life of @mrjoness3 #danieljones at two churches to stand with his family in mourning. We laughed, we sho nuff cried—men just as much as the women—and we spread the love he gave us all to each other to help us through. Beautiful fellowship this weekend with @erro44 @curtchambers @adamblackstone @dwiskingbeef_official @jermaine_parrish @colabolabooks @catalystmusic @djorenance @nyalagazelle @carmenrodgers @stixxtaylor @aliasboogie @bcockerham81 and more.

I spoke spontaneously at the wake to acknowledge the NYC/NJ formative period of his career where MD gigs for indies like me, @erro44 and the @sobsnyc #solvillage prepared him to play and MD stadium tours for the likes of @janetjackson and @erykahbadu who were also in the #friendshipwestbaptistchurch building yesterday. So so so so so many people came up to me and told me how deeply he loved and trusted me and talked about me all the time. My heart is full. As Badu said, we will NEVER stop speaking his name. And as Janet sang, one day we’ll be together again.

Thank you @friendshipwest and @dc3online for hosting his wake and funeral services. Thanks you to all the preachers who preached and soloists, choirs and praise teams who soothed our souls in song. May the healing begin. Thank you #dallas for raising this polite joyful man who grew up to cowrite songs for Rihanna,
Beyoncé, Michael Jackson, Timbaland, Justin Timberlake, DJ Khalid. He humbly graced the stages of the Grammys, the Oscar’s, the MTV awards, the Billboard and BET awards. Short in height, he stood tall alongside music royalty —always making others feel like Kings and Queens and acknowledging his mentors.

Daniel, you did it, bro. You truly touched the world and never forgot where you came from—always giving Glory to God who made a way for your #oakcliff reared talent. “I love you in a place where there’s no space in time/I’ll love for me life/you are friend of mine” as @donnyhathaway once sang. ❤️🙏🏿 #friendship #gordonchambers #adamblackstone #ericroberson #curtchambers #chinahblac #carmenrodgers

In the spirit of @mrjoness3 expansive musical diversity the NYC posse went to jam sessions at the home studio of @sputacular (of @snarkypuppy) and at @freemansrestaurant. We played ballads, freestyle R&B, funk and enjoyed the brilliance of some of #dallas finest musicians @rcwilliamsjr (of @rcandthegritz and the @erykahbadu band) and singer @thenathanmyers who also sang his heart out at both funeral and wake. #freemansrestaurant #nathanmyers #jamsession 

As #erykahbadu said, the musical community all over the world will NEVER stop saying the name #danieljones. Thank you #dallas #desototx #oakcliff for your warm welcome to us who loved him and traveled to pay tribute. And thank y’all for being local friends and musical family and mentors for 41 years to this brilliant and now ascendant talent. #gordonchambers #robertseawright #rcandthegritz #rcwilliams #chinahblac #missingyou #carmenrodgers

Who knew that this song would bring so many so much joy via IG? Thank you @tonedoesmusic for posting and friends @movingupward @easyevans1 and many more for sending it to me! They sure did prove it here!
#ifyouloveme #sayitdoitshowitproveit

Sooo grateful for this footage @ogtroynalls sent me two days ago and thankful that I had some of the shows I played with @mrjoness3 #danieljones on video  posted to YouTube to remember the fun we had adding some jazz and gospel flair to my live shows. I loved him on acoustic piano, his roots.

Always a sensitive intuitive supportive musician and an even BETTER friend. Loyal, uplifting and kind. Spoke my name with honor when I wasn’t in the room to so many. My most treasured and beloved memory of him was the day he called me 3 days after my major house fire in 2016 and organized the @sobsnyc #solvillage band led by @dwiskingbeef_official and host @erro44 to do a musical tribute to me. My heart was broken from fear and trauma and the musical medley of my songs uplifted me in a way that STILL brings tears.

Thank you my ascendant young heavenly brother from another mother. You made so many so proud and loved us with such purity. We will forever speak your name. #gordonchambers #friendship #thebluenotenyc

Happy heavenly 60th birthday big sister @whitneyhouston! Thank you for the joy your catalogue continues to bring the world. This soca remix in slide four gave me life recently at Brooklyn Street Fair! Thanks @superbizzee for the invite!

Countdown until your Foundation Legacy Gala tonight! Thank you for the good love you gave me every time I was in your presence. I’ll always have your back, just as I do in the bottom picture @smegsavvymarketing took and sent me. HBD also to my friend @iamulyssescarter, right hand to you in life and after transition as executive of the Whitney Houston Estate. Thank you Sir for our beautiful memories for decades. See you this evening!

#whitneyhouston #gordonchambers #yvetterussell #ulyssescarter #iwannadancewithsomebody

TBT: Sharing memories of working with @whitneyhouston has been one of the greatest honors of my life. A snippet of my 7-minute interview on @newshour a week after her passing. She lives on forever in my heart and in the melodies she left for millions. Happy heavenly 60th #whitneyhouston #gordonchambers #pbsnewshour

Grateful as always to be always greeted and treated as a family member by @whitneyhouston family. Great to party with a purpose with sister-in-love @mpathouston (President of the Whitney Houston Estate and former manager), brother Gary who sang joyously tonight, @donnakhouston, Ray Watson (Pats brother and #whitneyhouston former bodyguard) and niece @rayahhouston! A great gala it was awarding students en route to #hbcu colleges thrown by the #whitneyhoustonlegacyfoundation. #pathouston #garyhouston #whitneyhouston #whitneyhoustonestate

Also amazing to be in the room celebrating @whitneyhouston heavenly #60thbirthday with so many of her close friends and collaborators like #bebewinans @kimburrelllove (who both brought the house down), her former guitarist @jubu.smith and ensemble, her former PR @gwendolynquinnofficial (now also representing her Estate) and former producers @officialnarada and @harveymasonjr (President of #naras who present the Grammys). 

All the speeches were warm and the performances brought us to church. Bebe and Kim reminded us how much Whitney truly loved the Lord. I remember her praying for and with me in the studio and backstage at a John P Kee concert Pat took me to. It was powerfully anointing. Her Christian belief of to whom much is given, much is required continue via #thewhitneyhoustonlegacyfoundation. See whitneyhoustonfoundation.org to learn more and donate. Thank you @mpathouston and @primarywave for your work continuing her legacy. #gordonchambers #kimburrell #jujusmith #naradamichaelwalden #harveymason #whitneyhouston

TBT: Wow. Time flies! Happy 24th birthday to my nephew @wop.starr! Thank you for the joy, charisma and calming energy you bring to the Chambers/Ellis clans of 07666! Enjoy the day and stay blessed. #unclelove #leoseason #teaneckhighschoolalumni

FBF: One week ago, I packed my suitcase and boarded a plane to Dallas with a heavy heavy heart. I did not want to accept that my time on Earth with brother @mrjoness3 #danieljones had come to an end in the physical realm. His funeral services were uplifting but I was so sad inside. I tried my best to hide it and uplift everyone around me. It was inside that I cried, to quote the  @cecepeniston ballad.

Left there for Atlanta for the @whitneyhouston heavenly 60th birthday celebration and Foundation Gala. On the 48 hour countdown I saw friends and family I hadn’t seen in years and they made me smile so wide when i so needed it. Thank you to all my hosts: cousin @jodiawatson and boys MJ, Matthew, @dyllonburnside and Mom Chantae, old friends @octaviusterry and @masonmonroe, @drivemecra_z and @darrenmallett, @donnitacamille and #marvinbrooks. Wish I had more time in the city to see more of my folks, but enjoyed my quick run-around.

Life is truly about the “legacy of love”’as the gala was named. To my great surprise, the vinyl of “One Wish” (Whitney’s Xmas album I worked on) was in the gift bag alongside a tee shirt from the amazing songwriter/entrepreneur @travismalloy. Grateful to God to be loved here by the living and to have been loved by legends #whtineyhouston and #danieljones. Can’t wait to sing and break bread with them again in heaven whenever God calls me home. They came to do what they needed to do here on Earth. We must accept that.

Life is truly about leaving a “legacy of love”. Thank you Dallas and Atlanta for your happy meals and Southern Hospitality. And thank you Daniel and Whitney for the beautiful memories and #legacyoflove we share. ❤️🙏🏿

Yesterday I celebrated the 50th anniversary (and yes I was born in the Boogie-Down Bronx where it all began) with my bro producer-recording artist @dariendorsey visiting from LA at the @bklynlibrary celebration of @jayzz_official! What a legend #jayz is! Didn’t realize the magnitude of his contributions to the culture. He is the very embodiment of the American Dream in so many ways!

Brought back so many memories seeing the multi-track tapes of sessions at NYC top studios Hit Factory, Right Track, Sound on Sound, Quad with some of the top #hiphop producers that I wrote many R&B lyrics for (even singing on @naughtybynature4ever album) like #trackmasters and @kaygeenbn. RIP to the always kind #heavyd and #andreharrell of #uptownrecords, the label that truly understood that hip-hop and R&B were kissing cousins. 

Thank you #jayz for the pride you’ve brought to the borough I call home. Where Brooklyn at? Exhibit closes the end of October 23.

Welcome to the fifties @chinahblac! We’ve laughed and cried together. Grateful for it all. Thanks for being a true road trip ride-or-die chick for your loved ones. Come celebrate with the Brick City Leo Diva who has toured with icons @erykahbadu @missjillscott @chakakhan tomorrow at her event at @sobsnyc! Love you for life. Happy #fiftiethbirthday #chinahblac #gordonchambers #sobsnyc

Sunday Appreciation: God sends you exactly who’s for you at the appointed time. In 2009 on a fateful night, my drummer bro @rob_l_3 (9th panel) was visiting NYC. He told me that his bro producer @dariendorsey (who played a gig once with us in Baltimore) had graduated from @berkleecollege and had moved to NYC. We all decided to meet a jam session thrown by @natejonesonbass. That night I also heard @reallouiscato @coreybernhard play there and was blown away. #lepoissonrouge #livemusic 

I ended finishing up my 3rd album with @dariendorsey on beats and a lot of vocal production and a title track by @iamsteffreed. @iamsteffreed and @dariendorsey quickly became great friends as well. When I started touring with the Sincere album @reallouiscato @coreybernhard and (not pictured) @les.is.lrcfunk and @dginyard started playing me regularly. These gents were also recent grads of @berkleecollege and so supportive and professional. We began beautiful friendships. I have also done #vocalcoaching for #louiscato over the years and he’s singing his face off!

Scenes from @reallouiscato album “Reflections” release this weekend. He is now the MD of #latenightwithstephencolbert show. @coreybernhard played keys on Friday with him and does so also on the show. What a genius he is and so humble. Please also check out solo albums released by @iamsteffreed and @dariendorsey. So amazed by all their talent and work ethic. #danieljones often reminded of the impact I’ve made on younger musicians. This post is to let y’all know you inspire me just as much. Grateful for the love and respect you give me. #brotherhood 

Strength to @rob_l_3 who lost a brother and cousin in the last two weeks. I love you. God be with you. And daily prayers for the family and loved ones of @mrjoness3. RIP. Thank you @ogtroynalls for this BEAUTIFUL pic of us (last panel). #friendship

Knowledge is power! “Stop, look, listen to your heart, hear what it’s saying” as Thom Bell and Linda Creed wrote for the Stylistics.

Captured on candid camera this weekend by @dariendorsey and @fajohnson59 at the JayZ exhibit and in conversation with Alecia Johnson who inspires me! Great to see you this weekend @treniajohnson at the Johnson backyard joyfest in Jamaica, Queens. 

I love NYC and it’s adventurous, curious, youthful fun-in-the-sun loving peeps in all five boroughs.

TBT: Always a PROFOUND honor to inspire the youth of New York City. Thank you @readalliance for your incredible work as a nonprofit hiring college-bound teenagers to tutor elementary kids in reading. Without the words I read in poetry books I loved as a kid, I would never have grown up to become the songwriter, journalist and editor I became.

Congrats on your continuing work there @yvetteconcuatro, my successor at @essence who now proudly serves as Chief Strategist and Head of Programs and Partnerships for this wonderful organization. Thank you for leading me by example to give back to the community. Scenes from the 5th annual teen conference last Friday where I spoke for the second year in a row. This year the conference was covered by @pix11news!

To whom much is given, much is required. Each one, teach one. Grown ups, find causes that move your soul, and “get into, get involved” as James Brown instructed. Great day all! #gordonchambers #yvetterussell #wpixnews #jamesbrown #huntercollege #readalliance

Giving reflections of my #teaneckhighschool teenage years to the teens of NYC at last weeks @readalliance conference at @huntercollege: #readalliance #huntercollege 

I will always and forever call your names #donyalemorton #danieljones @mrjoness3 

Everyday is a gift. Share your stories and touch someone’s life. Shine your light. The next generation is watching. Be a blessing.#thiskittlelightofmine #gordonchambers #readalliance

TBT, 2001: I will never forget spending this glorious day in #bayshorelongisland to receive my first-ever #communityservice award from the  BayShore Schools Arts Eduction Fund alongside hip hop legends @yasiinbey (AKA #mosdef) and @therealdougefresh #dougiefresh and tap genius #savionglover. It was an honor to perform and speak to the youth that day. I will always stand up proud to inspire for the next generation. Enjoyed my fellowship immensely that day with these icons! #gordonchambers #bayshoreschools 

Happy #fiftiethbirthday #hiphop!

Wishing my keyboard wizard bro @shedrickmitchellofficial @shedrickmitchell a glorious 49th birthday today! Scenes from his show at @smokejazzclub this past Wednesday feat. Special guests @christiedashiell and @theaaronmarcellus who sang their faces off! Shed met @theaaronmarcellus at the @rongrantnfriends #villageunderground Sunday night #openmike where he served as MD for 20 years while touring with legends on Maxwell, Aretha and Whitney! Check out his jazz piano video recordings! 

He played and arranged much of my Surrender album, and produced my cover of “I Surrender All” featuring his anointed hands on Hammond B3. A genius of our time! I thank him eternally for introducing me to @mrjoness3 #danieljones I’m 2003 who he added to the band for my #bbkings record release concert, one of the happiest nights of my life. We miss you Daniel. So glad Shed brought you into my life. RIP.

Great fun last night in celebration of the documentary #timeofessence which finally debuts tonight on @owntv at 9 PM with episode 1 on the 70s. I’ll appear in episode 3 on the 90s on Sept 1st!

Great fun representing our former editor-in-chief @iamsusanltaylor who couldn’t be there with former coworkers fellow writer-editors turned authors @mamacheetahs @iammikkitaylor @blackamericanrunaway and @linda_villarosa! Throughly enjoyed working on this project with producer @4mzsharonb and meeting new #essenceventures CEO @wangawoman. 

Great to hear the director @chrischarlesscott and #essencemagazine owner @richelieudennis and brother @emmetdennis speak as well. Over 50 years and going of this brand that changed my life! Tune in for the next five weeks! #essencemagazine #gordonchambers #susantaylor #audreyedwards #mikkitaylor #lindavillarosa #deborahgregory 

Thank you @1princejamir for the red carpet interview and years of support!

Wowwww! Watched the first episode of #timeofessence a second time at home! So well done, and full of great backstory 1970s drama. Check this out out on-demand y’all and set your DVRs for the next four Friday nights at 9 pm on @owntv!

Thank you @1princejamir and @theknockturnal for this red-carpet interview at the premier party on Thursday. Thank you @oprah and @owntv for greenlighting this for TV viewing. And thank you sister @sidrasmithofficial for being the first call for my involvement on this project. Congrats Miss executive producer extraordinaire❤️🙏🏿 #gordonchambers #sidrasmith #essencemagazine #owntv

Enjoying the last weeks of Summer! Greetings from #marthasvineyard, a safe haven for Black families to vacation since the late 1800s and an island where Black intellectuals often give talks for travelers! Scenes from yesterdays book signing for @blackamericanrunaway #audreyedwards—my friend and former #essence coworker who also appears in the documentary #timeofessence on #owntv—thrown in the gorgeous hydrangea-filled garden of hostess media maven @csawyerspeak. Great fun with @purplegiraffe30, cousin Michele Lewis, Janine Brown, former #essence staff @taiiasmartyoung Lavon Leak and meeting local strangers with deep connections to this magical island #blackauthors President Obama and Skip Gates love so much. 
#oakbluffs #gordonchambers #marthasvineyard #booksigning
A great day with the Woodleys , Harper and Sage and the Truvillions! Annual family #blackjoy in #marthasvineyard with the Godchildren. Happy birthday @shellybellamy ❤️❤️

Always love learning from the little ones! Great morning walk with @differentheadspace19! Nuff respect to supermoms like her and @taraflorabella that balance motherhood and career so beautifully. #unclegordon #thegodfather #alongwalktowater

Black families have been vacationing on this magical island since the 1800s. Seeing the young ones in our family fly kites and run with the wild geese during this sociopolitical climate made my heart sing! Great to reconnect and walk and talk with friends @differentheadspace19 and @iammichelemorgan and meet new ones like @mrlewisspears (amazing husband, father, author and nonprofit leader and advocate for the Black male youth of #jerseycity via #kesmitofkings). It takes a village to raise Black children with healthy self-esteem in times like this. Thank you @taraflorabella @sheldonnoel06 and #marthasvineyard for having us. A joyous three day it was indeed! “We are the world/We are the children”

A gloriously happy birthday to @valeriesashford, 77 years forever young today! Thank you for all you and #ashfordandsimpson have done and all you #valeriesimpson and your @sugarbarnyc family continue you to do! Always big fun hosting here. We love your heart, your fashion, your passion for life! What joy your music and hospitality bring the world every day! #gordonchambers #nickashford #sugarbarnyc #aintnomountainhighenough #77thbirthday #livinglegend

Scenes from todays @djspinna set in honor of inspirations, beloved icons and supporters of my songwriting journey @michaeljackson and @prince hosted by @officialspikelee around the corner from my house at #fortgreenepark, across the street from where #spikelee lived for many years. Incredible danceathon with music-loving friends @tobiastruvillion and @iammichelemorgan and friendly strangers. 

#iwoulddieforyou brought a tear to my eye, remembering when a sister sang it at @mrjoness3 funeral a couple of weeks ago but I held it together to keep enjoying life as #danieljones would want me to. The last time I saw him in the land of the living was at a 80s party he performed at in Dallas that I sang at. One day I’ll see him again “laughing in the purple rain”

Thank you #djspinna who remixed one of my songs “Never Fall In Love” for your musical brilliance. Thank you @officialspikelee for doing something free of charge every summer in radically gentrified downtown BK for people’s joy. #michaeljacksonversusprince

Sunday Inspiration: on Whitney’s heavenly 60th birthday one month ago, I shared the stage spontaneously with @mpathouston #bebewinans and  @kimburrelllove for the encore song “Power Of Love” by #luthervandross. #ilovethelord #kimburrell 

In times like this we must STILL “love the Lord” who hears our cry. Prayers and justice for the lives shot down by racist hatred yesterday in #jacksonville Florida yesterday. @kimburrelllove sang this #richardsmallwood classic so beautifully in salute to our friend #whitneyhouston. HBD to the gospel legend. #virgoseason #gordonchambers #pathouston

A perfect Sunday it was yesterday celebrating 38 years of #blackexcellence at a fundraiser for the dance company I’ve had the honor and pleasure of singing with many times @evidencedance, founded by @ronkbrown718 and run with his partner @arcell_trece  in the Hamptons. 

Great friendship reunion with @purplegiraffe30 @jacquifrancis9 @shawnayoung.fwd @jehbk @doreenchambersinteriors @cerebral_women @iamcorambarry.

This event was created years ago by the late GREAT amazing @jjhamptons, and resuscitated 10 years later to honor her. I will miss my morning walks at #sagharbor beach with my friend. Her elegant son Brandon was in the building and spoke so poignantly about this Mom who we all loved so dearly who transitioned earlier this year. She dearly loved #evidencedancecompany who move their bodies to gospel, house and Fela with #blackjoy! Congrats to host committee members @reggievanlee and @jehbk! A day to remember indeed! #joycejackson #moderndance

Grateful for a personal showing of the art show “A Proof Of Being” today with friends from photo whiz and Jamaican-born wonderwoman @reneecoxstudio who I’ve had the honor of sitting for for a portrait. Love love love me some #blackexcellence in #thehamptons. Brava #reneecox 🇯🇲

TBT: enjoying the last days of summer! Thank you SO much to my hostesses @l_lewis1961 @loidanlewis @jehbk @vanliemptbrown! Great as always  to see you @reggievanlee @emckiss @shawnayoung.fwd @iamcorambarry And last on NOT least @jjhamptons we’ll NEVER forget you, and will love your son Brandon for the rest of our days. #brandonmullings Tomorrow is not promised y’all. Make memories and shower your peeps with love and joy! #thehamptons #sagharbor #friendship

Shoutout to friend and #vocalcoaching client @akwaekeemezi @yungdeadthing for making their debut as musical artist this weekend at the prestigious @afropunk stage! Proud to have supported this award-winning novelist on their transition to singing, MCing and live spoken word perform. Yes, y’all, I coach all genres and even public speakers. I inspire self-expression. Thank for the kind words in @wmag! And thank you @brandonvhixon for the introduction! #gordonchambers #afropunk #akwaekeemezi

Simplify hilarious! The joy this song continues to give the world never ceases to amaze me! Happy heavenly birthday @michaeljackson who’s group brought this to the world.
Thank you @thats_teeee! #sayitdoitshowitproveit #ifyouloveme #brownstone #gordonchambers

Tonight’s the night y’all! Please tune in and/or set your DVRs at 9 PM Friday to @owntv to view part 3 of the #timeofessence docuseries that EVERYONE is talking about. I’m interviewed in the 90s episode alongside friends and former colleagues I’ve had the pleasure of spending time with this summer in Martha’s Vineyard and Sag Harbor @blackamericanrunaway #audreyedwards @harriettecole @iamsusanltaylor @mamacheetahs #deborahgregory and the model I came to know then via @lloydboston who become  Hollywood royalty @boriskodjoe. As the only male editor on the team then, working on the men’s issues #boriskodjoe highlights was great fun! Check it out y’all! Also on #hbomax. Back down memory lane we go! Grateful how the chapter of my life that began at age 20 molded me! Also on @hbomaxes! #hbomax 

#gordonchambers #susantaylor #essencemagazine #harriettecole #marthasvineyard #sagharbor

Spending this long last Labor Day weekend of summer in the DMV! Great to see hospitable friends in Baltimore and DC. Thank you travel buddy @jacquifrancis9 (for planning dinner for @m.sabir_ward and #larrysatterfield and I) birthday boy @cookingwithkasean (happy 50th!) my ride-or-die @colabolabooks (for the lodging and shopping whirlwind joyfest)  @rob_l_3 (beautiful healing hang at the @lewismuseum and lunch) @sunnyjazzdc (for tix to see @gregoryportermusic at the #dcjazzfest) and DJ @summerloving71 (for inviting us to see you spin)! #dmv #friendship #reginaldlewismuseum

SUNDAY INSPIRATION: when someone shows you familial and professional empowerment for decades like @whitneyhouston did for me even a decade before I wrote and produced for her, you beam that light back on all you meet who sing and touch your soul!

What an HONOR to be in the building for this 20-year-old @_gabbysamone #whitneyhouston tribute concert this past Wednesday. She hit ALL the notes flawlessly and brought tears to my eyes of hope. Thank you SO much @nskirby @bmoreepicfam for inviting me to see your new hometown #baltimore starlet rock the night at her first ever sold-out headlining show at @keystonekorner! Her future is so bright! God is using her. Enjoy these performance clips and pics. Great to meet you @darinatwater Happy Sunday from the DMV! 

#gordonchambers #artistdevelopment #gabbysamone #carvercommunications #epicfam #keystonekorner

Scenes from a GLORIOUS weekend in the sunshine at the @dcjazzfest #dcjazzfest where friends @jacquifrancis9 @everybodyblack23 @jazeeee20 @everybodyblack23 and I throughly enjoyed jazz sets by @syberspace (featured with @orrin_evans), @terrilynecarrington and @samarajoysings—who was interviewed by my dear friend of 30-plus years @sunnyjazzdc! So so proud of #sunnysumter who I worked with years ago at @essence who is now the proud President of this jazz festival! Trivia fact: Sunny arranged my interview at @essence while I was still in college and I got the job 3 weeks after graduation! Thank you sis for always believing in me. Love you 4 life. #essencemagazine 

She hired me for the second year in a row to moderate a panel in the Caribbean influence on jazz. Had a wonderful time interviewing @omarsosamusic (Cuban pianist) and @ettienecharels (Trinidadian trumpeter and percussionist). Thank you @sunnyjazzdc and new friend @aaronlmyers for your hospitality at the gorgeous #dcwharf. A weekend of friendly faces and incredible music it was. Congrats to all who worked on the sold-out festival! #sysmith #omarsosa #ettienecharles #terrilynecarrington #samarajoy #orrinevans #gordonchambers

Saved the best for last during my Labor Day weekend in #dmv! Scenes from a post-Tuscany reunion breakfast yesterday with music lovers Jackson and Cooper, big brothers of Julian and sons of @thehouseofwink. They wanted to know how it was for me to host @jonbatiste at my house a couple of weeks ago for a video shoot!  We also walked to the Smithsonian to see some #africanart. 

Also did an impromptu masterclass with the teenage band #frequency. Auntie Phyllis @colabolabooks raises their drummer Dominic and is big sister to his high school band. Showed the sax player how to think like a singer. Big fun in Union Station!

Last and NOT least, scenes from the record release party of the band @attinshun and a pic with bass player Jarel who has been an MD for me for several DC shows with this unit. So proud to see them getting their own shine on with this project in between dates touring with @raheem_devaughn and others. Thank you @tone.walters for the invite. 

Uncle Gordon is always down to spread love into the next generation! Thank you for the hugs and nuff respect y’all gave me this weekend. Beautiful close of summer! #gordonchambers #unionstage #attinshun #mentorship #artistdevelopment #vocalcoaching

For black men, the chair is a safe, trustworthy and sacred space. Thank you for decades of cuts and supportive conversations to me and many. Happy fiftieth birthday to my groomer @donovandon19! Barber and stylist to Brooklyns finest! HBD #myjamaicanguy! Throwback with @amuid. Enjoy the day and many more memories and rivers to cross ahead! ❤️🙏🏿❤️👋💪🇯🇲🎵#fiftiethbirthday

Fun summer memory! That time I came to see @therakiemwalkerproject play at @melbasharlem on Harlem Week Sunday outdoors and they burst into #ifyouloveme then wifey Gloria (their lead singer) passed me the mike! Happy birthday to this joyful bandleader! Keep rocking my brother #rakeimwalkerproject #gordonchambers . Thank you #melbasrestaurant for supporting live music!🎵❤️

TBT: last week my whole body went into chills when @samarajoysings took us to church with a vamp of #steviewonder “Lately” which she remixed into the end of “Guess Who I Saw Today” at the closing set of the @dcjazzfest which she helped to sell out for the first time! Congrats to @sunnyjazzdc, Prez of #dcjazzfest, for reaching out to book her BEFORE her Grammy win! I’m officially now a super fan. Thank you @aaronlmyers for the last minute seat upgrade!

This young chauntese has such poise and amazing grace. What a star! Raised right in the Bronx where I was born by preachers and God-praising singing family who encouraged her to spread her wings and fly to the top off the jazz charts! God bless you #samarajoy. May you stay spiritually grounded as you soar to all the High heights God has planned for you. What a talent. “To be young gifted and Black”, as @ninasimone and @lorrainehansberryinitiative penned together. “Oh what a precious feeling!”

Thanks to all for your kind supportive words about my appearance last week in the 90s episode of #timeofessence. I left the magazine full-time in 1997. During the 2000s, I continued doing some consulting and freelance writing for the magazine and proudly performed at the 2006 Essence music festival! The magazine also wrote about me more than once. 

Check out tonight’s episode at 9 pm on @owntv about 2000-2010. The whole 5-part series (which concludes next week) is also available on @hbomaxes. Proud to be a part of helping tell the @essence story. #gordonchambers #essencemagazine #essence

@barkimmusic1 said it beautifully: “you knew @mrjoness3 loved you if he introduced you to other people he loved.” The last time I hung with the late great #danieljones in NYC, he brought @stixxtaylor who he was so proud of over to my house to meet me. They were both on tour with @therealmaryjblige. Stixx also plays for @usher and @justinbieber.

Drum whiz #stixxtaylor is one third of a band called #trapjazz that is featured in a new documentary on @hulu about their life building a movement when not on the road with other artists. What a beautiful soul he is, what friendship their trio share, and what a beautiful film on young musicianship. Check it out and be moved by these church-reared young men from Atlanta who are bringing jazz to a new generation! 

Also grab your tix to see me and many others perform at @sobsnyc on Sept. 20th in tribute to our beloved friend now with God. So proud I witnessed your growth from teenager to husband, father, MD and mentor to other greats. Love you eternally Daniel Your spirit lives eternally in those you loved. 🙏🏿

#gordonchambers #sobs #trapjazz #hulu #musicdocumentaries #danieljones

We are honoring our brother Daniel Jones aka @mrjoness3 Sept 20th at @sobsnyc.  That stage was home for him.  If you ever played with him, sang with or in front of him, or enjoyed what he showered you with, come join us.  Goto www.sobs.com for tickets. 

The Collective w/ @chinahblac in Conjunction w/ @sobsnyc  will be celebrating an amazing life.. 
The LIFE of Musical Director, Producer, Songwriter, Artist, and SOBs Family, MR. DANIEL JONES!!!!

Music By @Dwiskingbeef_official and the @dwcollectiveny 

Hosted By: Mr. Eric Roberson @erro44 w/ Special Guests

Join us as we celebrate Daniel’s life and musical legacy.

“So tell me, who are the people in your neighborhood” was the theme song from the Mr. Rogers show way back when. A beautiful weekend spent with my community leading neighbors it was! Scenes from the grand opening of the Je T’Adore exhibition at @yanceyrichardsongallery in Chelsea. Paintings inspired by the anonymous Black female erotica of yesteryear in Jet Magazine. “I wanted to reclaim and beautify these ladies” #mickalenethomas told me. Proud to know one of the premiere black female artists of our time and #vocalcoach to her lovely daughter Junya! Thanks sis for having me.❤️👏

Congrats to neighbor Pastor @iam_alexwilliams of @iimchurch who’ve I’ve known since his teenage years. This third generation minister is all grown up and got married this weekend at a ceremony attended by the Mayor @nycmayor #ericadams. Reception held at the iconic  @riversidenyc where I hung with friend @iamkenpen. #pastoralexwilliams 

Last on not least, a joyous and meaningful rooftop birthday celebration with salon owner Carol Thomas of @justbecausehairnyc who spreads beauty and grace in all she does! I am inspired by these three who remind me why, after all it’s changes, I still love me some #fortgreene Brooklyn! #lovethyneighborhood

TRIBUTE: Grab your tix for the @sobsnyc tribute to the legacy of #danieljones! Our brother @erro44 will host. I will be one of the special guest performers. Please join us for this VERY special #solvillage, the show he MD’d for many many years. RIP our dear bro. Showtime: Sept. 20th, 8 PM. Tix available at Www.sobs.com. Peace!
#gordonchambers #ericroberson #sobsnyc

Scenes from lesson #1 with new #vocalcoaching student Trini-born jazzy-soul singer @iamdwightthomas! He discovered I live in Brooklyn after listening to my inaugural interview on old friend #ledisi “Looking Back” podcast where she interviews colleagues about craft! Nothing like the feeling when singers tell you you inspire them to hit notes they never imagined they could sing. DM me for lesson inquiries. Thank you Brother Dwight. Let’s soar high. 

Thank you Led (who always affectionately calls me “Teacher”) for all you do. You’re always beaming bright light! #gordonchambers #vocalcoach #artistdevelopment

Flashback Friday: always a great honor to coach another #vocalcoach when asked. Scenes from Tuesday’s birthday show by @wailwithshannahrae who shared originals and inspirational covers by Tina, Whitney and a rare @chakakhan cut called “Love Has Fallen On Me.” 

Big big fun with a mike toss at the end to @albiegray who I’ve also coached. Always beautiful supportive musical family spirit at the house that @ashfordandsimpson built. Thank you @valeriesashford for setting the tone of love that rules this the room. “It Seems To Hang On” indeed!
#gordonchambers #vocalcoaching #sugarbarnyc #supperclub #chakakahn #shannahraevocalstudio

The day producer @4mzsharonb interviewed me for #timeofessence, model and mogul @the_real_iman was also in the building to sit for candid camera. I’ll never forget the day she took little ole me to lunch when I was the 23-year-old entertainment editor to talk about a nonprofit initiative she wanted to partner with the magazine on. Maya Angelou also took me to lunch once at the Hotel Algonquin “where Jimmy and I used to meet” (she said, referencing Mr. Baldwin of course!). Wish I had a pic!

I’ll also NEVER forget @iamsusanltaylor introducing me to @steviewonderlegacy for the first time after he received the Essence Award. Always grateful for the trust this job gave me to represent the company with Black royalty. Tune in tonight for the final episode for the docuseries at 9 pm on @owntv or on @hbomaxes.

#gordonchambers #iman #steviewonder #susantaylor

Grazing in the grass! An epic day trip with @superbizzee it was yesterday to and from the @diabeaconny celebrating @iamsteffreed with his posse! HBD to the musician, activist and @unionseminary grad student who loves museums and nature like we do! Enjoy 44!! Thank you #diabeacon for a space that elicits conversation, verbal relations and relaxation (like @missjillscott once sang)! #steffreed
